'''辉煌号卫星'''（Glory）是[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]在2011年发射的一颗[[地球探测卫星|地球探测卫星]]，卫星的任务是在700公里高空分析火山、森林火灾、烟囱和排气管所排出的[[悬浮颗粒|悬浮颗粒]]<ref>{{cite news|title=NASA发射地球探测卫星 追踪悬浮颗粒对气候影响|url=http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2011/2/244224.shtm?id=244224|accessdate=2011-02-23|newspaper=科学网|date=2011-02-23|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918145640/http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2011/2/244224.shtm?id=244224|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=NASA's Glory Satellite Arrives At Vandenberg Air Force Base for Launch|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/Glory/news/launch-site-arrival.html|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2011-02-23|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309153702/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/Glory/news/launch-site-arrival.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该卫星原定于2011年2月23日在[[范登堡空军基地|范登堡空军基地]]通过[[金牛座運載火箭|金牛座XL]]（Taurus XL）火箭发射升空<ref>{{cite web | title =Launch Schedule | publisher =NASA | url =http://www.nasa.gov/missions/highlights/schedule.html | date =December 8, 2010 | accessdate =2010-12-17 | archive-date =2019-01-29 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190129135246/https://www.nasa.gov/missions/highlights/schedule.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>，后因故推迟了数日<ref>{{cite web  | title =NASA Assessing New Launch Dates For The Glory Mission  | publisher =NASA  | url =http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/feb/HQ_M11-056_Glory_Delay.html  | date =2011-02-24  | accessdate =2011-03-03  | archive-date =2011-02-27  | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110227015856/http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/feb/HQ_M11-056_Glory_Delay.html  | dead-url =no  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title =NASA's Glory Satellite Scheduled for Launch on March 4 | publisher =NASA | url =http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/mar/HQ_M11-041_Glory_Launch_Day.html | date =2011-03-04 | accessdate =2011-03-04 | archive-date =2011-03-04 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110304001055/http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2011/mar/HQ_M11-041_Glory_Launch_Day.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。<br>

2011年3月4日，火箭升空六分钟后，[[整流罩|整流罩]]没有正确的与火箭分离，卫星未能进入预定轨道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-12551861|title=Nasa Glory mission ends in failure|publisher=BBC News|4=|date=2011-03-04|accessdate=2011-03-04|archive-date=2011-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110305052725/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-12551861|dead-url=no}}</ref>，整体坠入[[太平洋|太平洋]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-03-04/234922054975.shtml|title=美国地球观测卫星发射失败坠入太平洋|publisher=新浪网|date=2011-03-04|accessdate=2011-03-05|archive-date=2011-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110308043614/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2011-03-04/234922054975.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/Glory/main/index.html|title=Glory|publisher=[[NASA|NASA]]|access-date=2011-03-04|archive-date=2011-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811042140/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/Glory/main/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这次失败与两年前美国嗅碳卫星坠落事故十分相似<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/2009-02-24/23582854835.shtml|title=美国嗅碳卫星发射失败坠入南极附近海域|publisher=新浪科技|date=2009-02-24|accessdate=2011-03-04|archive-date=2009-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227101408/http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/2009-02-24/23582854835.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

